00:39:21,164 --> 00:39:24,964
<i>April showers will come, so they say</i>

436
00:39:25,435 --> 00:39:28,927
<i>But they don't and it's May</i>

437
00:39:29,673 --> 00:39:33,541
<i>You're about to forget the whole thing</i>

438
