440
00:40:26,329 --> 00:40:30,663
<i>And the obvious reason</i>
<i>Is because of the season</i>

441
00:40:31,067 --> 00:40:34,969
<i>Ma Nature's lyrical</i>
<i>With her yearly miracle</i>

442
